    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Wood of the species Nothofagus solandri, native to New Zealand.  It is brown in color and known for its high strength and durability.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
